(19, 'Brooklyn Beckham\'s Dior suit set the bar high for wedding day fits', '/static/posts-images/Beckham%20Family.webp', '<p>This weekend&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/fashion/article/brooklyn-beckham-pepe-jeans\">Brooklyn Beckham</a>&nbsp;and Nicola Peltz tied the knot at a star-studded ceremony (the Williams sisters, the Spice Girls and Gordon Ramsay attended) on Miami&#39;s Palm Beach, which reportedly cost a whopping &pound;3.5 million. With 27-year old Peltz in a custom Valentino couture gown designed by Zendaya&#39;s go-to designer Pierpaolo Piccioli, which took a year and multiple trips to Rome to create, it was down to Beckham to pull off something equally as spectacular.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And that he did. While we&#39;re used to seeing&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/gallery/david-and-victoria-beckham-couple-dressing\">David and Victoria Beckham</a>&#39;s eldest offspring in baggy skater jeans,&nbsp;<em>Peaky Blinders</em>-esque baker boy caps and Carhartt coach jackets (he &quot;wears the same thing everyday&quot;, he told&nbsp;<em>GQ</em>&nbsp;in 2021), for his nuptials Brooklyn Beckham went to French maison Dior, and family friend Kim Jones, for help.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Image may contain Brooklyn Beckham David Beckham Clothing Suit Overcoat Apparel Coat Human Person and Fashion\" src=\"https://media.gq-magazine.co.uk/photos/6253fc729e6b92a44dd39386/master/w_1600%2Cc_limit/Beckham%2520Family.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The British designer, who also heads up Fendi womenswear, has been the artistic director of Dior menswear since 2018 and has dressed the Beckham clan on countless occasions, so the partnership was an obvious and easy choice. David wore a bespoke morning suit to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/gallery/royal-wedding-guest-list-best-dressed\">Meghan Markle and Prince Harry&#39;s wedding</a>&nbsp;in 2018, while the entire Beckham brood have sat FROW at Jones&#39; catwalk shows in custom Dior looks.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What&#39;s more, Dior is newly-married Beckham&#39;s designer of choice for formalwear. &ldquo;For the red carpet it&#39;s always Dior,&rdquo; he told us last year. &ldquo;The suits the brand makes fit me well. I have these big, broad shoulders that I struggle to find a suitable jacket for. Dior&#39;s got it down. I have one that they&#39;ve given me and I wear when I need to.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For Beckham&#39;s wedding, Jones and Dior created a super chic, custom black wool peak lapel tailcoat, which was cut to perfection and adorned with a silver chain at the front. It came with matching, straight-cut trousers and a white cotton wing-tip collar shirt with plastron piqu&eacute; and high-shine, jewellery buttons.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By way of accessories Jones outfitted Beckham with a white bow tie and pocket square, while on his feet the 23-year old wore black polished leather derbies, which were stamped underfoot with Dior branding. A unique touch came by way of a bespoke label, designed by Peltz, which was sewn into Brooklyn&rsquo;s jacket. Rather nicely, Brooklyn wasn&#39;t alone in wearing Dior, either. David, Romeo and Cruz showed their support for Brooklyn by wearing matching black tuxedos, which were created in Paris by the French label.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 7, '2022-04-12 05:43:59.185537', '2022-04-12 05:43:59.185537', '2022-04-02 00:00:00.000000'),
(20, 'Britney Spears Says \'I am Having a Baby\' Leaves Fans Confused', '/static/posts-images/0c5eb7fb70a74aaf81bb248e07f6e8eb_xl.jpg', '<p>Britney Spears may have revealed some exciting news, but her post has fans confused more than anything ... wondering if she&#39;s pregnant with a child or just a food baby. Spears got the Internet talking Monday when she posted, &quot;I lost so much weight&hellip;</p>\r\n', 8, '2022-04-12 05:45:33.600426', '2022-04-12 05:45:33.600426', '2022-02-11 00:00:00.000000'),
(21, 'Kendall Jenner Explained Why She \"Always Had A Feeling\" That Kourtney Kardashian And Travis Barker W', '/static/posts-images/sub-buzz-13404-1649711561-4.webp', '<p>Kourtney Kardashian and Travis Barker seem like a ride-or-die couple at this point. (But they&#39;re not actually married yet.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maybe you&#39;ve been surprised at the strength of their relationship &mdash; but you know who isn&#39;t? Kendall Jenner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In a recent interview with People, Kourtney revealed that Kendall basically predicted her relationship with Travis years ago.In a recent interview with People, Kourtney revealed that Kendall basically predicted her relationship with Travis years ago.</p>\r\n', 8, '2022-04-12 05:47:38.022501', '2022-04-12 05:47:38.022501', '2022-02-03 00:00:00.000000');
